 python3-typer,
 ffmpeg
Description: CLI video player that renders video as ASCII art in the terminal
 asciiv plays video files directly in your terminal window by converting
 each frame into ASCII characters. It supports audio playback via FFmpeg
 and pygame, with controls for scale, speed, volume, looping, and custom
 character sets.
 .
 Requires FFmpeg to be installed for audio extraction and sync.